-- CITIES / LOCAL JURISDICTIONS — 2024-tax-year resident rates (Phase 3 ships these as 2026 rates;
-- most locality rates have not changed materially for 2026. Re-validate annually).
-- Source: user-provided local_income_tax_rates.csv (compiled from city/county DOR pages).
-- MFS and HOH reuse SINGLE schedule (Phase 3 simplification).
-- Special structures NOT seeded (cannot encode in our flat-bracket schema):
--   CO_AURORA: Flat $/month occupational privilege tax, not bracket-able
--   CO_DENVER: Flat $/month occupational privilege tax, not bracket-able
--   CO_GLENDALE: Flat $/month occupational privilege tax, not bracket-able
--   CO_GREENWOOD_VILLAGE: Flat $/month occupational privilege tax, not bracket-able
--   CO_SHERIDAN: Flat $/month occupational privilege tax, not bracket-able
--   IA_ALL_SCHOOL_DISTRICTS_VARIES: 0%-20% surtax on state tax; varies by district; cannot encode
--   NJ_NEWARK: Newark payroll tax is employer-paid on employee wages, not a resident income tax
--   NY_YONKERS: Yonkers resident tax is 16.75% surcharge on NY state tax; cannot encode in bracket schema
--   OH_OHIO_SCHOOL_DISTRICTS_200: Generic placeholder for ~200 Ohio school districts
--   OR_LANE_COUNTY: Employer-paid payroll tax, not resident income tax
--   OR_PORTLAND: Portland Arts Tax is a flat $35/year fee, not bracket-able
--   OR_TRIMET_DISTRICT: Employer-paid payroll tax, not resident income tax
--   PA_MOST_OTHER_MUNICIPALITIES_2500: Generic placeholder, not a specific locality
--   PA_MOST_MUNICIPALITIES_LST: Generic placeholder, not a specific locality
--   WV_CHARLESTON: Flat $/week service fee, not bracket-able
--   WV_HUNTINGTON: Flat $/week service fee, not bracket-able
--   WV_PARKERSBURG: Flat $/week service fee, not bracket-able
--   WV_WEIRTON: Flat $/week service fee, not bracket-able
